title: Forager
content:
Forager is a type of profession where you must find raw ingredients required to make potions.

As foraging can take your character into higher level zones with dangerous creatures that will aggro onto your character, it is recommended to level your Guard skill in tandem with your foraging skill in order to be able to adventure into dangerous areas to acquire these valuable resources.





Capes are unlocked by achieving various milestones in leveling of a profession and can be purchased from Daguer at The Cloakroom located in Hopeport.

Location (# of Nodes).text: Old Street East (3), Old Street West (3)

Uses.text: (Cooking) Cod and Chips / Sausage and Mash

Location (# of Nodes).text: Old Street West, Old Street East
